WEBVTT

00:00:58.068 --> 00:01:01.159
Most of those individuals
had spent most of their lives

00:01:01.183 --> 00:01:02.668
in long-stay hospitals.

00:01:02.692 --> 00:01:04.157
This is a long time ago.

00:01:05.021 --> 00:01:08.548
And for them, autism was devastating.

00:01:09.395 --> 00:01:12.038
They had profound
intellectual disabilities.

00:01:12.558 --> 00:01:13.792
They didn't talk.

00:01:14.310 --> 00:01:15.629
But most of all,

00:01:16.217 --> 00:01:21.146
they were extraordinarily isolated
from the world around them,

00:01:21.170 --> 00:01:23.007
from their environment

00:01:23.031 --> 00:01:24.904
and from the people.

00:01:25.392 --> 00:01:28.219
